import EmmaPic from '../../assets/images/em2.jpg';

export const aboutObjOne = {
    id: 'about',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'About Me',
    headline: `Hi! My name is Emma, and I'm a Makeup and SFX artist.`,
    description: "I have 5 years of experience specialising in beauty and media makeup. I've trained in barbering, film and tv. Have a look at my portfolio and CV. If you're interested in working together, don't forget to send me a message!",
    buttonLabel: 'Portfolio',
    imgStart: false, 
    imgEm: '../../assets/images/em2.jpg',
    alt: 'Emma Barua',
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: false
};
